38:37.899 --> 38:44.738
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

38:56.126 --> 38:59.210
- [laughs]
That was cool.

38:59.254 --> 39:02.339
- All right, Keith,
your blade required two slices

39:02.382 --> 39:03.590
