39:05.552 --> 39:09.137
And then on the backhand slice,
cut nicely on the sandbag.

39:09.181 --> 39:10.847
I like the guard.

39:10.891 --> 39:12.682
I like the details
that you put into your blade.

39:12.726 --> 39:15.602
This, sir, will cut.
- Thank you.

39:15.645 --> 39:17.312
- Next up, the strength test.

39:17.356 --> 39:19.356
Dave.

39:19.399 --> 39:22.150
- Gentlemen, to test the
strength of your weapons,

